    "media:imagetext": "SPURAN:\nSALTLAKE CITY\nSAN FRANGIOGU\nSALINAS\nSANTA BARE\nVIDALIA\nBAKERSFIELD\nSEE THE\nUSA\n•UNITED BRANI NICKCHANGE SEKVICE\nTRANSCONTINENTAL NONSTOP JET SERVICE\nSEATTLE /TACOMI\n/ PHILADELPHIA\nMOLINE-ROCKAISLAND-DAVENPOR\nDAYTON\nCOLUMB\nCHARLESTON. W.\nL-KINGSPORT-JOHNSON C\nGREENSBOR\n•ON-SALEM\nCHATTANOO\nCHARI\nATLANTA\n• DUOTUN\nNGFIELD\nPROVIDENC\nNEW TORY\nNEWARY\nOWN-BETHLEHEM-EASTON\nPHILADELPHIA\nWASHINGTON\nPORTINENS HAMPTON\nNORFOLK-PORTSMOUTH\nRALEIGH-DURHAM\nDALLAS\nNEW ORLEAI\nSPETERSBUR\nWEST PALM BEACH\nUnited's new Family Plan saves you\n⅓ for your wife, ⅔ for your children\nHere's how it works weekdays - From noon Mon-\nday through noon Friday, head of family pays full jet\nCoach fare. Wife pays ⅔ the regular fare, children two\nthrough 21, ⅓ the regular fare.\nNew weekend plan - From 12:01 a.m. Saturday\nthrough noon Sunday, head of family pays full jet Coach\nfare. Wife pays ¾ the regular fare, children two through\n11, ½ the regular fare, and children 12 through 21, ¾\nthe regular fare.\nUse your Bank Americard, Diners Club, Carte Blanche,\nAmerican Express or United's Fly Now Pay Later plan to\ncharge your trip.\nEffective now to all United cities except Honolulu",
